data.description: Amazing Property loaded to the hilt with additions! This property includes a 3bd 2bth home with a 3 car garage, fully enclosed RV garage, 2 story 1bd 1bth apt with wood deck overlooking horse arena, and a studio apartment w/2 car garage. The yard is fully fenced with auto gates in the brick portion for an elegant entrance. Animal lovers dream land with multiple stables covered and open, large arena with viewing stands, cool down arena, 3 well built metal chicken coops,Rv hookups, and 4 storage shipping containers that make up the Carport. Assumable VA Loan at 3.5% !
